item.title: Need Help With Port Forwarding
item.dc:creator: @X_F_U_R_Y_X X F U R Y X
item.description:
@X_F_U_R_Y_X wrote:

Don’t know, but find your ip address by using ipconfig with command prompt (Default Gateway) then put it into your address bar in a browser, then if it asks you for a password then it’s usually something like:
admin
password
admin
pass
admin
123

Or something like that… or contact the service with customer support and then ask them… thats the last resort if you really want a server without hamachi…

Good luck… :(, I have a warning now, for double posting… does it go away? or no?
